•Enhancements for how you can transfer money.
•Want to be able to view your account balance without opening the app? You can now with our new Balance Widget! It can be added to the Today Center by scrolling to the bottom of the page, tap "edit," and add the new widget.
•And of course the normal behind the scenes minor enhancements and bug fixes!
